In /opt/custom, the special_bin is owned by user and setuid, but not owned by root. This likely limits its power somewhat.

I will check ownership and permissions recursively for all files in /opt to see if there are any root owned setuid files. I will do:

find /opt -type f -perm -4000 -exec ls -l {} \;

